name: PortlandWaste
0:
”Alexa, open Portland Waste”
”Alexa, ask Portland Waste when does my garbage come?”
”Alexa, tell Portland Waste my address is 12804 E Burnside Street”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: portland waste
des: This skill ties into the Portland Maps API to deliver waste collection information to residents of Portland, Oregon. To deliver accurate collection details, this skill needs to collect your address either through granting it access to the address stored on your device, or you can set your address through the skill
